{"tid":1589597,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門衝突19歲男子被控參與暴動　獲准保釋","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T11:01:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9392c0ea527ce8ef9216350ed4964ae745051a2","tid":1589597,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】上周六屯門衝突，一名19歲學生被控參與暴動罪提堂，獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n19歲李浩銘步出法院，多名聲援市民打開傘陣，護送他離開。他被控上周六即本月21號，在屯門屯匯街時代廣場外參與暴動，暫時毋須答辯。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官陳炳宙指，被告當時穿有遮蔽臉部的衣物，手腳都有護甲，並持有護盾，背包又被搜出約百條索帶及行山杖等，認為他重犯機會高，亦有潛逃風險，批准他以五千元現金保釋，但要交出所有旅遊證件，亦要遵守宵禁令，並禁止在屯門出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=363768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363768&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66dOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=46b5695b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363768&h=5bf7a8a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=363768</a>"},{"pid":"e788493b0ec4f06c3a2b43f56afc252113e676ac","tid":1589597,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a17cd3d8bd3cfc68800b68bb4b24ec7a78dce1d3","tid":1589597,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"}]}